WEBVTT

00:13:31.840 --> 00:13:35.280
And if worst case scenarios
do come to pass,

00:13:36.520 --> 00:13:40.416
we'll have to learn
to forgive ourselves for not knowing

00:13:40.440 --> 00:13:43.136
or for not asking the right questions

00:13:43.160 --> 00:13:45.880
or not finding the right treatment.

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:48.496
We should always assume

00:13:48.520 --> 00:13:51.160
that someone we love may be suffering,

00:13:51.880 --> 00:13:54.496
regardless of what they say

00:13:54.520 --> 00:13:55.760
or how they act.

00:13:56.720 --> 00:13:58.840
We should listen with our whole being,

00:13:59.800 --> 00:14:01.000
without judgments,